{"tid":624381,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Snapdragon 660 都未有乜電話用，咁快就話出snapdragon 670","createTime":"2018-04-10T19:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T08:30:12.000Z","uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"614609d2a5c7536b0e0e179971c78d170cf97988","tid":624381,"uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T19:31:51.000Z","msg":"660 變得垃圾???<br />\n<br />\n其實驍龍670處理器已經曝光了一段時間，最早可以追遡到2017年8月，不過直到目前為止都未有搭載該處理器的手機推出，昨日根據XDA的報導，小米最少有兩款產品將會搭載驍龍670 處理器，同時有關該處理器的規格資料更詳細曝光。<br />\n<br />\n驍龍670基於10NM技術設計，8核心處理器，框架方面並非使用常見是4+4 Big Little設計，而是採用命為Kryo 300的2+6設計，當中包括兩顆A75大核及6顆A55細核。驍龍670細核主頻最高1.7 Ghz，大核則最高達2.6Ghz；GPU方面就採用Adreno 615，標準頻率範圍在430 Mhz至650 Mhz之間，動態則最高達700 Mhz。<br />\n<br />\n其他方面，驍龍670下載速率最高達1Gbps，最高支援2K解像度，支持UFS2.1/eMMC 5.1！最後小米Note 4好大機會升級致驍龍670，至於另外哪一款手機，暫時就未有更多資料。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/033129_0caf095230dd08617aa4382d24ed2b1f.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F033129_0caf095230dd08617aa4382d24ed2b1f.PNG&h=858a7dd2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8430d5f1ea82540cf0bf5950064fd8b54359cf6b","tid":624381,"uid":63311,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T20:06:47.000Z","msg":"過渡產品？"},{"pid":"4460440c581102a80b528277dfb54d218cddc6a6","tid":624381,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T23:44:17.000Z","msg":"670量產未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68b94003cd616d1723395d6c0205be892d004dc","tid":624381,"uid":658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T04:51:05.000Z","msg":"大把660<br />\n不過專攻大陸姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6276f3d032d9061fb46f80dc0b6a24374b29efd","tid":624381,"uid":165184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T05:44:41.000Z","msg":"660一開始疑似俾oppo掃哂<br />\n<br />\n之後有d廠冇得用<br />\n轉左用630<br />\n(moto x4)<br />\n<br />\n而630市場反應又疑似唔錯<br />\n（電源控制方面, 岩做公司機）<br />\n<br />\n所以好似冇乜廠用"},{"pid":"4856ff371c5ba752420455cb6603a190455b28c4","tid":624381,"uid":115511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T08:30:12.000Z","msg":"唔用大陸牌子，等有其他先考慮，完"}]}